    • Constructor Detail

      • GammaEnergyFWHMCalibrationFrame

        public GammaEnergyFWHMCalibrationFrame(GammaAnalysisFrame mf,
                                       java.lang.String[][] dataMatrix,
                                       java.lang.String[] columnNames,
                                       java.lang.String[][] dataMatrixAccurate)
        Constructor. Before creating object of this class, the ROIs must be present via insert Roi.
        Parameters:
        mf - GammaAnalysisFrame object
        dataMatrix - data matrix with 2 significant digits containing some data such as ROI id, ROI centroid, and ROI FWHM. It is used just for display data.
        columnNames, - the column names for the calibration table.
        dataMatrixAccurate - same as dataMatrix but with full precision. This is used in calculations.
